---
flowchart TD
    A["猜数游戏"] -->|输入1| C("随机生成答案")
    A -->|输入2| D("结束游戏")
    C --> E("猜数")
    E -->|猜对| F("尝试次数，正确答案")
    E -->|猜错| G("告知与答案大小关系")
    G -->|记录尝试次数| E
    F --> A
    R(告知规则) --> A
```



```c
#include <stdio.h>
#include <time.h>
#include <stdlib.h>
int main()
{
    int r = 2;
    printf("\tGuess NUMBER game\t\n\n\t    [1]Start\t\n\n\t    [2]EXIT\t\n");
    scanf("%d", &r);
    while( r <= 1 ) // 开始游戏
    {
        srand((unsigned int)time(NULL));
        int answer = rand() % 101 + 1; // 从1-100随机选取一个数字
        int x = 0;
        int n = 1; // 用于记录尝试次数的变量
        printf("\tGuess a NUMBER from 1 to 100\t\n\nI'll tell you whether IT is bigger or smaller\nin comparison with the NUMBER i selected\n\n");
        printf ("Enter Your ANSWER: ");
        scanf("%d", &x);
        while(x != answer) // 猜错开始循环
        {
            if(x < answer) // 输入小于答案
            {
                printf("Your answer is Smaller\n");
            }
            else // 输入大于答案
            {
                printf("Your answer is Bigger\n");
            }
            printf("Try again: ");
            n++;
            scanf("%d", &x);
        }
        printf("You've tried %d times, the Answer is %d\n", n, answer);
        printf("[1] PLAY AGAIN\n[2] EXIT.....\n");
        scanf("%d", &r);
    }
    return 0;
}
```

在 ***《软件技术基础》*** 这门刚开始学的课程中老师讲的算法的**时间复杂度**，讲了**大O表示法（Big O Notation）**，举了一些例子

- **O(1) 常数时间**
- **O(log n) 对数时间**
- **O(n) 线性时间**
- **O(n log n) 线性对数时间**
- **O(n^2) 平方时间**
- **O(2^n) 指数时间**
- **O(n!) 阶乘时间**
  现在我还是不会算一些循环的时间复杂度
